A proselyte harness m can be obtained after completing the Slug Menace quest by buying it from Sir Tiffy Cashien in Falador. It may be opened to obtain Proselyte armour.

The set contains: Proselyte sallet, Proselyte hauberk, and the Proselyte cuisse.
